node.title: "Family Reunion" actress Jaida Benjamin found safe
node.description: The 27-year-old had last been seen Saturday in Studio City, L.A. police say.
node.content: ["A 27-year-old actress who went missing over the weekend was found safe early Tuesday morning, CBS Los Angeles reports.", "Los Angeles police confirmed that Jaida Benjamin was located in Studio City at around 2:30 a.m.", "It's unclear how she was found or why she disappeared.", "Benjamin was last seen on Saturday a few blocks away from where she was found.", "Her television credits include \"Family Reunion,\" \"Insecure\" and \"Criminal Minds.\"", "For Breaking News & Analysis Download the Free CBS News app"]
